an></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">綠茶婊</span> &mdash;&gt; <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死八婆 / 臭閪</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">裝/裝b</span> &mdash;&gt; <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">扮晒蟹 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">土豪</span> &mdash;&gt; <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">闊佬</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">高富帥/白富美</span> &mdash;&gt; <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有錢仔/女</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">富二代</span> &mdash;&gt;<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 二世祖</span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多繼續加落去<br />\n希望大家<span style=\"color: violet;\">養成</span>一個<span style=\"color: violet;\">習慣</span><br />\n以後一見到有on9仔用左呢啲字一定要屌<br />\n屌到佢大肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2834614b91103ccae5f895569dcd705438e1475e","tid":1993264,"uid":165332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:58:20.000Z","msg":"咪撚再用啊dllm"},{"pid":"425f26effda17c8eeb8e65a12290fd3278ca131b","tid":1993264,"uid":165332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T15:58:36.000Z","msg":"習慣成自然啊屌你哋"},{"pid":"a93023eb85e44ca2b1c321a746eb2410e9bbe120","tid":1993264,"uid":49900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:00:13.000Z","msg":"土豪用暴發戶意思上比較貼切"},{"pid":"da2fb276fe43ec0000a462b725ba003b1f77975f","tid":1993264,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2851293fd6919827ea48b38675f6fb7969e30a7a","tid":1993264,"uid":165332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a93023eb85e44ca2b1c321a746eb2